1 (3) A FORMER REGISTERED MASSAGE PRACTITIONER WHO FAILS TO
2 APPLY FOR REINSTATEMENT OF THE REGISTRATION WITHIN 5 YEARS AFTER THE
3 REGISTRATION EXPIRES MAY BE REINSTATED ONLY BY MEETING THE LICENSING
4 REQUIREMENTS IN EFFECT FOR OBTAINING A NEW LICENSE UNDER THIS TITLE AND
